rt.DeepCopyInto` and `TargetPort.DeepCopy` -- confirms DeepCopy was generated for the shared type\n\n### `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go` (33 lines)\nContains `GroupVersion`, `SchemeBuilder`, `AddToScheme`, Kind constants, `SchemeGroupVersion` alias, and `Resource()` helper -- all referenced in the AR-003 delta-spec.\n\n### `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go` (3 lines)\nPackage-level code generation markers:\n```go\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package\n// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\npackage v1alpha1\n```\n\n---\n\n## 4. TODO, FIXME, or Deferred Work Markers\n\n**No TODO, FIXME, HACK, XXX, or deferred markers were found** in either:\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/`\n\nHowever, the **tasks.md** file shows all task items as **unchecked** (`- [ ]`), indicating the implementation work is tracked but not formally marked as complete in the task checklist.\n\n---\n\n## 5. Git History\n\n**No git commits** were found referencing \"AR-003\", \"CRD 共享\", or \"shared_types\" in commit messages. The repository has commits but none are related to the AR-003 change set. This suggests AR-003 is either:\n- A planned/proposed change not yet committed\n- Part of uncommitted working tree changes\n- Tracked only through the design document files (not via git commits)\n\n---\n\n## Summary of All Relevant Files\n\n| File Path | Role |\n|-----------|------|\n| `design.md` | Root-level AR-003 design document (English) |\n| `.sdd_prompt.md` | SDD prompt triggering AR-003 design |\n| `changes/AR-003/proposal.md` | Formal proposal (Chinese) |\n| `changes/AR-003/design.md` | Detailed design spec (Chinese) |\n| `change